Emelec                   Ecu  Barcelona (Ecuador)                Ecu   0-0  0-1  0-1
* x 2nd leg replay 9/13 in Santiago after match in Medellín (won 2-0 by Atlético Nacional) had been annulled after a protest by Vasco complaining of pressure on the referee (death threats) by local druglords


Round: Semi-Finals 
* (9/5 & 12)


Atlético Nacional        Col  Olimpia (Paraguay)                  Par   1-2  3-2  4-4x 1-2p
River Plate              Arg  Barcelona (Ecuador)                Ecu   1-0  0-1  1-1  3-4p
x 1st leg played 9/20 in Santiago de Chile due to the incident surrounding the
  quarterfinal between Atlético Nacional and Vasco da Gama; 2nd leg 9/26


Round: Final 

* (10/3 & 10)
